description.narrative: Local authorities in target areas have adopted child-friendly strategies, improved knowledge of the situation of children and enhanced capacity to design and deliver integrated and equitable supply of services., which contributes to Access To Justice, Child Protection And Emergencies, Child Protection Systems, Data And Child Protection, Evaluation And Research, Human Rights Institutions, Justice For Children, Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children (Covid), Violence, Exploitation And Abuse.
